---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 组织wiki
permalink: /组织wiki/
---
<section class="collection-page collection-page--wiki" aria-labelledby="wiki-index-title">
  <header class="page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">术语词典</p>
    <h1 id="wiki-index-title">组织 wiki</h1>
    <p class="lede">从这里查找知识花园中反复出现的基础概念。</p>
  </header>
  <div class="collection-list cards">
    {% for term in collections.terminology %}
      {% if term.kind == 'wiki' %}
        <a class="card" href="{{ term.url | url }}">
          <p class="eyebrow">组织术语</p>
          <h2>{{ term.name }}</h2>
          <p>查看这个概念的解释、比喻和用途。</p>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
